## App store assets

Before your first EAS build, generate placeholder icons and splash screens:

```bash
cd mobile
python assets/create-placeholders.py
```

This creates `icon.png` (1024×1024), `adaptive-icon.png`, `splash.png` (2048×2048), and `favicon.png`
using only Python stdlib — no Pillow or ImageMagick required.

To generate final branded assets from a source image:

```bash
# Requires: brew install imagemagick  (macOS)
bash assets/generate-assets.sh
```

